    {
      "id": "PopularPost24513",
      "post_content": "@Fragskull:\n  \nMany older enchantments like [Kismet](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Kismet), [Lifetap](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lifetap) or [Soul Barrier](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Soul Barrier), which were not designed with multiplayer environments in mind, were upgraded to comprise all your opponents. This is not true for certain artifacts which would probably be too strong with such an errata ([The Rack](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=The Rack) and [Black Vise](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Black Vise) come to mind), other artifacts like [Fellwar Stone](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fellwar Stone) got a similar errata or rather a clarification in their rules text.",
      "posted_by": "holgir",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost24513\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">@Fragskull:\r<br/>Many older enchantments like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Kismet\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Kismet\">Kismet</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lifetap\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lifetap\">Lifetap</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Soul Barrier\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Soul Barrier\">Soul Barrier</a>, which were not designed with multiplayer environments in mind, were upgraded to comprise all your opponents. This is not true for certain artifacts which would probably be too strong with such an errata (<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"The Rack\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=The Rack\">The Rack</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Black Vise\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Black Vise\">Black Vise</a> come to mind), other artifacts like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fellwar Stone\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fellwar Stone\">Fellwar Stone</a> got a similar errata or rather a clarification in their rules text.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '24513'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2612\">holg