    {
      "id": "PopularPost59763",
      "post_content": "The flavor text can be argued to be a bit in collision with the mechanic as library is the player's \"memory\" from where they dig up spells.  \n  \nBut the card, without these very minor things, is great and the flavor is better than in most cards.",
